                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(center)\">2.</p>\n            <p>in the learning that God granted me. I say “The fear of thy teacher, etc.”<lb/> “The\n                Torah of my teachers and my superiors” — “The fear of heaven” —<lb/> “A man's\n                livelihood is set for him”. And so I trust in God and must<lb/> complain that a man\n                like you who is known as a God-fearing man should<lb/> have so little influence. I\n                may be writing to a good friend and I ex-<lb/>pect that you will deal kindly with\n                me... but it is not possible to<lb/> remain inactive.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I should like you to send this letter to <persName>Jacob\n                    Friedman</persName>,<lb/> the Mohel. You will receive through the post either\n                one set of holi-<lb/>day prayer books or <sic>??</sic>. The house is easy to find.\n                    <persName>Pappe</persName> knows it.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Your servant ready to serve you,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Jonah of the house of Bondi</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"On the margin of the first page\">I am adding a report about the meeting for the\n                Sunday school.<lb/> Please publish it</p>\n            <pb n=\"Envelope\"/>\n            <p>\n                <persName>Rev. Isaac Leeser</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                <placeName>Penn</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>1227. Walnut St</placeName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p32z1392w/canvas/p3"
                }
